snippet.textDisplay:
Sometimes, you hear a song like 'Jhol' and it brings back everything  memories, feelings, and the kind of love that never really fades. It’s been 11 years, and though we never got the ending I dreamed of, she’s still a part of me. Life took us on different paths, but my heart still holds onto those moments we shared. She always wanted someone who fit the world her family imagined for her maybe that’s why she let go. It’s strange how a single song can make you feel everything all over again  the love, the loss, and the 'what ifs.' Maybe that’s just how some stories go, written in our hearts but never on paper. Sometimes, the moon feels distant, like someone calling out from FAR, but never quite reaching... like FAR-hin away, but close within... RUH-ul and the heart still hold on.
Sweety💕
